articles.title: Swiatek's Australian Open journey ends with a positive outlook - WTA Tennis
articles.description: Iga Swiatek's No.1 ranking will remain intact after her third-round loss at the Australian Open, but the 21-year-old says there's work to be done ahead of February's Middle East swing.
